question: Will Donald Trump join Parler before Inauguration Day?
description: This is a market on whether Donald J. Trump will join Parler prior to January 20th, 2021, at 12pm EST. The market will resolve to Yes if Donald Trump joins Parler (https://parler.com/) and has an official account, verified as him, with at least one post by the resolution date. It will resolve to "No" otherwise.
